Tom Neal https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tom_Neal 0 Thomas Carroll Neal Jr. (January 28, 1914 – August 7, 1972) was an American actor and boxer best known for appearing in the critically lauded film Detour and Club Havana, having a tryst with Barbara Payton and later committing manslaughter.
